  "texts": [
    "For the selection of these subfields and lead compounds, we took into account both the importance of the subfields and the necessity of selecting these particular compounds.",
    "With regard to the subfields, we chose four areas: cardiac toxicity, hepatotoxicity, enhanced water solubility, and metabolic stability.",
    "These are urgent issues in lead compound optimization and are also the major factors affecting drug recall [32].",
    "For the drugs, we selected paclitaxel, 10-hydroxycamptothecin, buspirone, and paroxetine as candidate lead compounds, as these are well-known or widely used antitumor drugs, anxiolytic drugs, and antidepressants.",
    "Additionally, during the selection process, we considered the performance of lead compound optimization before and after modifications."
